lyrics:
[Verse]
In the forest, we gather round
To share stories as the fire crackles sound
With mugs raised high, we take a cheer
United by friendship, and a love for beer

[Chorus]
We meet to drink beer in the forest once every month
At the fire with the boys we tell stories and have fun
Underneath the stars, our laughter fills the air
In this timeless tradition, we find solace and care
